    "abstract": "",
    "citationApa": "Giraudeau, Mathieu, Sepp, Tuul, Ujvari, Beata, Renaud, François, Tasiemski, Aurélie, Roche, Benjamin, Capp, Jean-Pascal, Thomas, Frédéric (2019). Differences in mutational processes and intra-tumour heterogeneity between organs. Evolution, Medicine, and Public Health https://academic.oup.com/emph/article/2019/1/139/5512491",
    "citationBibtex": "@article{Giraudeau2019differences-in-mutat,\n  title={Differences in mutational processes and intra-tumour heterogeneity between organs},\n  author={Giraudeau, Mathieu and Sepp, Tuul and Ujvari, Beata and Renaud, François and Tasiemski, Aurélie and Roche, Benjamin and Capp, Jean-Pascal and Thomas, Frédéric},\n  journal={Evolution, Medicine, and Public Health},\n  year={2019},\n  url={https://academic.oup.com/emph/article/2019/1/139/5512491}\n}",
