    "axis": "agents",
    "abstract": "In this paper, we introduce a concept of pseudo $\\mathcal {S}$-asymptotically ω-periodic (PSAPω) solutions, we establish some new composition theorems. By using the roughness theory of exponential dichotomies and the contraction mapping, some sufficient conditions are obtained for the existence and uniqueness of PSAPω solutions (abbreviated in EPCA) for some difference and differential equations with piecewise constant argument.",
